    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The drivetrain remains robust, benefiting from a recent VANOS system service and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral G-loads. Power is delivered to the asphalt via a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip and turn-out. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the suspension geometry remains true, and the hydraulic steering rack offers the telepathic feedback these chassis are known for. A mechanically sound, high-performance icon ready for its next enthusiast owner.",
